---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>td — task tracker for AI agents</title>
    <meta name="description" content="SQLite task tracker for AI agents. Single bash script." />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      
      :root {
        --bg: #fff;
        --fg: #111;
        --muted: #666;
        --border: #e5e5e5;
        --code-bg: #f7f7f7;
        --code-fg: #111;
        --green: #22863a;
        --font: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        --mono: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
      }
      
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        :root {
          --bg: #0d1117;
          --fg: #e6edf3;
          --muted: #8b949e;
          --border: #30363d;
          --code-bg: #161b22;
          --code-fg: #e6edf3;
          --green: #7ee787;
        }
      }
      
      html {
        font-family: var(--font);
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--fg);
        font-size: 22px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      
      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
      }
      
      main {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 720px;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      
      .intro {
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      
      .intro a { color: var(--fg); }
      
      .install {
        display: block;
        background: var(--code-bg);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--code-fg);
        overflow-x: auto;
      }
      
      .examples {
        background: var(--code-bg);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }
      
      .examples .line {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      
      .examples .cmd {
        color: var(--green);
        min-width: 320px;
      }
      
      .examples .comment {
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      
      .note {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      
      .note code {
        font-family: var(--mono);
        background: var(--code-bg);
        padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      
      footer {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
      
      footer a { color: var(--fg); }
      
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        html { font-size: 18px; }
        body { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start; padding-top: 3rem; }
        .examples .line { flex-direction: column; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .examples .cmd { min-width: auto; }
        .examples .comment { margin-left: 1rem; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>td</h1>
      
      <p class="intro">A task tracker for AI coding agents. I liked <a href="https://github.com/steveyegge/beads">beads</a>, but it became more than I wanted. So I made this. One bash script. SQLite. No setup.</p>
      
      <code class="install">curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alosec/td-world/main/install.sh | bash</code>
      
      <div class="examples">
        <div class="line"><span class="cmd">td create "fix auth bug" -p 1</span><span class="comment"># priority 1</span></div>
        <div class="line"><span class="cmd">td list</span><span class="comment"># show all</span></div>
        <div class="line"><span class="cmd">td move fix-a1b2 in-progress</span><span class="comment"># change status</span></div>
        <div class="line"><span class="cmd">td close fix-a1b2</span><span class="comment"># done</span></div>
        <div class="line"><span class="cmd">td dep add fix-a1b2 api-c3d4</span><span class="comment"># blocked by</span></div>
        <div class="line"><span class="cmd">td ready</span><span class="comment"># unblocked tasks</span></div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="note">Also installs <code>tv</code> — an fzf viewer with table and kanban modes.</p>
      
      <footer><a href="https://github.com/alosec/td-world">GitHub</a></footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
